{"tid":955031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英文女師甜上表特　私照太「兇猛」！網民：想師生戀","createTime":"2018-12-25T05:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T17:43:01.000Z","uid":147522,"like":415,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a0a8218dd6f8be4900ffc8139d77561d09b108","tid":955031,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6bKsZko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6bKsZko.png&h=4a624032&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8y57Zko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8y57Zko.png&h=79dd344c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvBSq0p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvBSq0p.png&h=573986f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有這樣的英文老師，學生真的很幸福！<br />\n<br />\n有網友在今在PTT「表特板」分享一正妹英文老師美照，照片中的正妹老師穿著一席粉色無袖連身裙認真教書，氣質相當優雅，而她的私照更是驚人，幾張低胸照片大方展現「兇猛」好身材，配上甜美的笑容，讓鄉民們紛紛暈船，留言直呼「為啥我以前的英文老師都是大嬸」「為什麼我以前英文老師不是長這樣」「可惡 我想學英文了」「老師我喜歡妳啊」<br />\n<br />\n原來這名正妹老師叫做「Ruby」，目前在國北教修讀課程教學所博士，也在台北某大學擔任講師，因為出眾的外表常常受邀參加各大綜藝節目，在網路上已累積不少粉絲。"},{"pid":"40708368e9f8559e95a666d041e12bb26269b022","tid":955031,"uid":227393,"like":131,"dislike":73,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞</span>"},{"pid":"c3b74f28227d5ea479e5fa228f27e386162350f1","tid":955031,"uid":10680,"like":26,"dislike":27,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fe911366d776c2d85dcd87ee0a564a3eb4974f1","tid":955031,"uid":73613,"like":337,"dislike":11,"score":326,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:57:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd687df8bb3d8d6de6594c5de3bf32bb5f850fd8","tid":955031,"uid":72009,"like":35,"dislike":16,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:58:25.000Z","msg":"又咪俾鬼仔當母狗中出<br />\n<br />\n係咁yes yes yes"},{"pid":"46365e1fbc2430728b8a6b3602d832e34f8d27f8","tid":955031,"uid":25163,"